      '\n> **Current**: This document describes test and mock exam features.\n\n# Tests & Mock Exams\n\nAspiron provides comprehensive assessment through chapter tests and full-length mock exams.\n\n## Test Types\n\n### Chapter Tests\n\n- Cover single chapter\n- 20-50 questions\n- 30-60 minutes\n- Topic-specific\n\n### Sectional Tests\n\n- Cover multiple chapters\n- 30-60 questions\n- 60-90 minutes\n- Section-specific\n\n### Full Mock Exams\n\n- Complete exam simulation\n- Full question count\n- Real exam duration\n- All subjects\n\n## Exam Features\n\n### Real Exam UI\n\n- Similar interface to actual exam\n- Navigation palette\n- Question numbers\n- Time display\n- Submit button\n\n### Exam Controls\n\n- Start exam\n- Pause (limited)\n- Submit\n- Exit\n\n### During Exam\n\n- Cannot go back (optional)\n- Timer countdown\n- Question progress\n- Review marked questions\n\n## Exam Integrity\n\n### AI Proctoring\n\nDuring mock exams:\n\n- **Tab Switching Monitoring** - Tracks active tab\n- **Answer Speed Detection** - Flags unusual patterns\n- **Pause Detection** - Monitors extended pauses\n- **Focus Score** - Overall attention metric\n\n### Integrity Features\n\n- AI disabled during exams\n- Copy/paste blocked\n- No external tools\n- Transparent monitoring\n\n### Integrity Output\n\nAfter exam:\n\n- **Focus Score** - Attention metric\n- **Integrity Indicators** - Any concerns\n- **No Punishment** - Trust-first approach\n- **Personal Report** - For self-improvement\n\n## Post-Exam Analysis\n\n### Score Report\n\n- Overall score\n- Section-wise breakdown\n- Topic-wise performance\n- Accuracy percentage\n\n### Time Analysis\n\n- Total time taken\n- Time per question\n- Time management insights\n- Suggestions for improvement\n\n### Mistake Patterns\n\n- Common error types\n- Topics with most mistakes\n- Conceptual gaps\n- Pattern identification\n\n### AI Recommendations\n\nAI provides:\n\n- What to study next\n- Topics to revise\n- Practice questions\n- Video recommendations\n\n## Exam Modes\n\n### Practice Mode\n\n- No time limit\n- Review during exam\n- Solutions visible\n- AI assistance available\n\n### Exam Mode\n\n- Timed\n- No review during\n- Solutions after submission\n- AI disabled\n\n### Both Modes Available\n\nStudents choose based on:\n- Learning vs. assessment goal\n- Practice needs\n- Comfort level\n\n---\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- [Practice Quizzes](/docs/practice-quizzes) - Learn about practice quizzes\n- [AI Proctoring](/docs/ai-proctoring) - Understand integrity monitoring\n- [Test Analysis](/docs/test-analysis) - See detailed analysis\n- [Revision Mode](/docs/revision-mode) - Learn about review features\n',
