      "\n> **Current**: This document describes the context-aware AI chat feature.\n\n# Context-Aware AI Chat\n\nAspiron's AI chat provides contextual assistance across videos, notes, and quizzes.\n\n## AI Chat Features\n\n### Context Awareness\n\nAI knows your:\n\n- **Exam** - JEE, NEET, or PGT\n- **Subject** - Your chosen subject\n- **Topic** - Current learning topic\n- **Timestamp** - Position in video\n- **Notes** - Your personal notes\n\n### Cross-Feature Integration\n\nAI chat is available in:\n\n- **Videos** - Explains current video content\n- **Notes** - Enhances your notes\n- **Quizzes** - Explains after submission\n- **Tests** - Post-test analysis\n- **Forum** - Community Bot integration\n\n## Chat Capabilities\n\n### Concept Explanation\n\n- Simplify complex topics\n- Explain in multiple ways\n- Use examples\n- Relate to other concepts\n\n### Note Enhancement\n\n- Summarize your notes\n- Find related concepts\n- Suggest additions\n- Improve clarity\n\n### Quiz Help (After Submission)\n\n- Explain why answer is correct\n- Break down solution\n- Suggest related practice\n- Identify gaps\n\n### Test Analysis\n\n- Review test performance\n- Identify weak areas\n- Suggest study plan\n- Recommend resources\n\n## AI Boundaries\n\n### What AI Does\n\n- Explains concepts you don't understand\n- Simplifies difficult topics\n- Gives examples\n- Helps you learn\n\n### What AI Does NOT Do\n\n- Take tests for you\n- Generate answers during exams\n- Copy content from elsewhere\n- Replace your thinking\n\n## Using AI Chat\n\n### Access Points\n\n- Floating chat button\n- Topic-specific AI\n- Note enhancement\n- Quiz explanation\n\n### Conversation Flow\n\n1. Ask question\n2. AI considers context\n3. Provides contextual answer\n4. Suggest related topics\n5. Offer further help\n\n### Best Practices\n\n- Be specific in questions\n- Ask follow-up questions\n- Request examples\n- Use for understanding, not shortcuts\n\n## AI and Learning\n\n### Learning Focus\n\nAI is designed for:\n\n- Understanding concepts\n- Filling knowledge gaps\n- Providing examples\n- Supporting recall\n\n### Not a Shortcut\n\nAI does NOT provide:\n\n- Direct answers to questions\n- Copy-paste solutions\n- Exam answers\n- Homework completion\n\n---\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- [AI Recall Check](/docs/ai-recall-check) - See memory-aware revision\n- [Practice Quizzes](/docs/practice-quizzes) - Understand quiz AI features\n- [Community Bot](/docs/community-bot) - Learn about forum AI\n- [Test Analysis](/docs/test-analysis) - See AI analysis features\n",
