    content:
      "\n> **Current**: This document describes the AI Recall Check feature - Aspiron's key differentiator.\n\n# AI Recall Check\n\nAI Recall Check periodically assesses what you've remembered and guides targeted revision.\n\n## What Is Recall Check\n\n### Definition\n\nAI Recall Check asks you to:\n\n- Explain concepts in your own words\n- No MCQs or multiple choice\n- No marks or scores\n- Focus on retention\n\n### How It Works\n\n1. AI identifies concepts you've learned\n2. Calculates when you'll start forgetting\n3. Sends recall reminder\n4. You explain in your own words\n5. AI evaluates your understanding\n6. Provides targeted suggestions\n\n## Memory Awareness\n\n### Forgetting Curve\n\nAI tracks:\n\n- When you learned each concept\n- How well you performed initially\n- Time elapsed since learning\n- Predicted forgetting point\n\n### Proactive Nudges\n\nBefore you forget:\n\n- AI sends recall reminder\n- Suggests specific topics\n- Estimates retention level\n- Recommends review time\n\n## Recall Process\n\n### During Recall Check\n\n1. AI presents topic\n2. You explain in your own words\n3. AI evaluates your explanation\n4. Identifies gaps\n5. Suggests targeted review\n\n### AI Evaluation\n\nAI assesses:\n\n- **Remembered** - Full understanding\n- **Partially Forgotten** - Some gaps\n- **Forgotten** - Needs review\n- **Misunderstood** - Incorrect concept\n\n## After Recall Check\n\n### Results Summary\n\nYou see:\n\n- Concepts remembered\n- Concepts partially forgotten\n- Concepts forgotten\n- Overall retention score\n\n### Targeted Suggestions\n\nAI provides:\n\n- Exact video links (with timestamps)\n- Relevant notes\n- Focused quizzes\n- Related test sections\n\n### Guided Revision\n\nInstead of overwhelming review:\n\n- AI prioritizes what matters\n- Breaks revision into chunks\n- Suggests specific resources\n- Tracks improvement over time\n\n## Recall Frequency\n\n### Smart Scheduling\n\nAI schedules recalls based on:\n\n- Concept difficulty\n- Initial understanding\n- Time since learning\n- Your available time\n\n### Not Too Frequent\n\nRecall checks are:\n\n- Respectful of your time\n- Based on actual need\n- Optional reminders\n- Never forced\n\n## Benefits\n\n### Active Recall Over Passive Review\n\n- You produce answers, not just recognize\n- Strengthens memory\n- Identifies gaps early\n- More effective than re-reading\n\n### Personalized Revision\n\n- Targets your weak areas\n- Maximizes study efficiency\n- Reduces wasted time\n- Improves retention\n\n### Long-Term Learning\n\n- Combat forgetting curve\n- Build lasting knowledge\n- Reduce cramming\n- Improve exam performance\n\n---\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- [Revision Mode](/docs/revision-mode) - Learn about revision features\n- [Context-Aware AI Chat](/docs/context-ai-chat) - Understand AI chat\n- [Test Analysis](/docs/test-analysis) - See post-test insights\n- [Progress Tracking](/docs/progress-tracking) - Understand metrics\n",
